# Keep the Docker build context small and reproducible. The Dockerfile copies only the manifests +
# packages/shared + apps/web, but excluding these speeds up context transfer and prevents host
# node_modules / prebuilt dist from leaking into the image (everything is rebuilt in-container).
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/build
**/.git
**/.turbo
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/*.log

# Mobile-only artifacts (the web build never needs them).
.expo
**/.expo
**/.expo-shared
apps/mobile/android
apps/mobile/ios

# Local env / editor cruft
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
.vscode
.idea
.DS_Store
